channel.title: Auto Cache Downloader Help [PI] BrokenX
channel.description: I need some help with auto cache downloader. Whenever I load up my webclient it says Connecting to File Server then a second after it says Error Loading...Please Report!. When I manually add the cache to the C drive it works perfectly though. If someone could help me through teamviewer that'd be awesome. Thanks

item.title: Auto Cache Downloader Help [PI] BrokenX
item.dc:creator: @No_Life2 No Life
item.description:
@No_Life2 wrote:

This error often occurs when you don’t give the CacheDownload.java file the right link to your uploaded cache.

First of all, zip the files INSIDE the cache folder.

Upload it using dropbox.com.

Then get the PUBLIC LINK, or DIRECT DOWNLOAD LINK and use that to download the cache.

Message me if you need in-depth help.
